Class Robot

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • actor.Actor
        • actor.Robot

  • public class Robot
extends Actor
    Models Robots in worlds. Robots can move places and carry Things only if powered on and controlled by a computer operated by a person.
    Author:
    Andrew Dallow
